      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities are performed on the same device geometry and within the same operating envelope as the intended CPB use conditions.",
      "rationale": "Validation activities used the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow conditions. The validation domain overlaps substantially with the intended use envelope. Relevance of validation to the decision context is confirmed at MRL 2."
