      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; FDA experimental dataset used as-is with documented provenance.",
      "rationale": "Statistical characterization of test sample variability is not required at MRL 2. The FDA generic pump experimental dataset has documented provenance and has been used extensively in the literature as a reference benchmark."
