    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions is accepted at Model Risk Level 2. All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 with documented justification. Predicted hemolysis indices agree with FDA experimental data within 15% across the CPB operating envelope, supporting the claim that the model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II device. The assessment team concludes that the computational model provides adequate credibility for the intended regulatory submission purpose.",
